r />\n無一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf112164df61c82987eb51a7df8104beec6639fb","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係絲打<br />\n我以我經驗 喪搽甘油 full住佢 <br />\n我亦有聽過巴絲用死海鹽full都得 觀塘有得買<br />\n不過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得你真係可以用鹽水消毒下個春袋 然後再搽嘢 <br />\n再係頂唔順 去藥房買類固醇膏 同佢講濕疹膏重劑量啲嘅<br />\n因為我都有支 薄薄地搽好啦 唔好搽太多 <br />\n止痕掂</blockquote><br />\n絲打都係天生有濕疹？<br />\n有試過去藥房買d粉紅色細細包既消毒藥水消毒過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死海鹽係咪真係work，平時落海水都會周身紅晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係保濕用？<br />\n唔敢搽類固醇係春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有副作用</blockquote><br />\n我係15歲個陣 嫲嫲煮左成碟蟹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企無人食自己一個對曬 咁就出事 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能死海鹽始終都係刺激皮膚 紅可能正常 你可能睇下舊post <br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=LV&amp;message=6394773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum5.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DLV%26message%3D6394773&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2Ff1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6eacfcaf\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=LV&amp;message=6394773</a><br />\n<br />\n甘油係保濕滋潤 我平時唔加水直接搽 係辛苦啲但起碼第二日無咁痕</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己對晒d蟹，d蟹咁毒緊係啦<br />\n唔夠膽用死海鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見有人話會仲嚴重左<br />\n點解搽甘油會辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為油淋淋同我搵保鮮紙保住full 會出水 <br />\n屋企偏方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我用保鮮紙點包住個春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1150cd0b06d32384558af2662b6a2435389f4ac0","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我平時濕疹一返發，就會用無比滴<br />\n「那」到飛起，但一定唔會再痕<br />\n<br />\n方法就俾左，試唔試就自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前試過，之後個春袋有菌<br />\n原來無比滴個海綿頭好多菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a231ad77bfcc382ec9dbfed31570833859f886d","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果啲係陰囊濕疹，我自己之前都飽受困擾。最緊要沖涼時沖涼液唔好掂到你個春袋，之後最好攞風筒吹下條j，尤其係d隙位，保證佢全乾先好著底褲，之後底褲質地要好，痕就要人手，真係忍唔住先去搽藥膏。</blockquote><br />\n巴打而家點，打算轉着孖煙通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682b0eb7ab37be3b697d8f2ae66e4031776a40d8","tid":156281,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>果啲係陰囊濕疹，我自己之前都飽受困擾。最緊要沖涼時沖涼液唔好掂到你個春袋，之後最好攞風筒吹下條j，尤其係d隙位，保證佢全乾先好著底褲，之後底褲質地要好，痕就要人手，真係忍唔住先去搽藥膏。</blockquote><br />\n巴打而家點，打算轉着孖煙通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家好轉好多，我真係受困擾幾年，之前晚晚臨訓都R到出血，第二日結焦，沖涼掂到水就&ldquo;拿&rdquo;到仆街嗌救命。<br />\n雖然明知好大獲，但都控制唔到自己咁係咁卒係咁R，越R越巢皮。<br />\n係近兩年的起心肝解決佢。依家雖然未完全斷尾，但都好咗好多，係可能四五日先痕一次咁，但都無當時咁劇烈，可以忍到既程度。<br />\n至少依家唔會影響生活。以前日頭做做下野會痕到忍唔到，搞到要得登去廁所R。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a51adad2c8226f4fa4311696213870e29db029","tid":156281,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"著裙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6780ba4bbd3cf67dba0445ce19644660561af","tid":156281,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果啲係陰囊濕疹，我自己之前都飽受困擾。最緊要沖涼時沖涼液唔好掂到你個春袋，之後最好攞風筒吹下條j，尤其係d隙位，保證佢全乾先好著底褲，之後底褲質地要好，痕就要人手，真係忍唔住先去搽藥膏。</blockquote><br />\n我都係用風筒吹，毛巾唔夠乾"},{"pid":"3e7e0c8ba776fe545852b4a121e92371b662ed6d","tid":156281,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/164805_e7ef308e2584c0734cb92a31ccc984cd.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F164805_e7ef308e2584c0734cb92a31ccc984cd.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2Ff1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=14fe25ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/164805_e7ef308e2584c0734cb92a31ccc984cd.jpg[img]</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚痕"},{"pid":"a3d946d787c146b48ba72fcd9b7e50283199cda3","tid":156281,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比佢一個乾爽既環境</blockquote><br />\n但冬天唔通着短褲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時着開長牛仔褲</blockquote><br />\n着瀨屎款jogger / sweat pants 好d?"},{"pid":"c488866631576e93d762d64dde54fc100c0b5265","tid":156281,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身冇生過濕疹,爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n濕疹有後天...運氣話黎就黎"},{"pid":"f23afcd4903c2e64c6345e822a64a20402757341","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T08:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/164805_e7ef308e2584c0734cb92a31ccc984cd.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F164805_e7ef308e2584c0734cb92a31ccc984cd.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2Ff1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=14fe25ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/164805_e7ef308e2584c0734cb92a31ccc984cd.jpg[img]</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚痕</blockquote><br />\n巴打你腫左一舊野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />btw 打返慎入"},{"pid":"08d593021df63218bb85bca7cce21f016b21b1f6","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果啲係陰囊濕疹，我自己之前都飽受困擾。最緊要沖涼時沖涼液唔好掂到你個春袋，之後最好攞風筒吹下條j，尤其係d隙位，保證佢全乾先好著底褲，之後底褲質地要好，痕就要人手，真係忍唔住先去搽藥膏。</blockquote><br />\n巴打而家點，打算轉着孖煙通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家好轉好多，我真係受困擾幾年，之前晚晚臨訓都R到出血，第二日結焦，沖涼掂到水就&ldquo;拿&rdquo;到仆街嗌救命。<br />\n雖然明知好大獲，但都控制唔到自己咁係咁卒係咁R，越R越巢皮。<br />\n係近兩年的起心肝解決佢。依家雖然未完全斷尾，但都好咗好多，係可能四五日先痕一次咁，但都無當時咁劇烈，可以忍到既程度。<br />\n至少依家唔會影響生活。以前日頭做做下野會痕到忍唔到，搞到要得登去廁所R。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家唔單止春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條丁都有少少好乾咁樣"},{"pid":"615272d752b8e9bac441230c8423045aa6a3dc03","tid":156281,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"幫人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友佢生左幾年，當時睇過家庭同專科，都係俾藥膏搽，冇為意係類固醇，依家搽到個春袋左右兩截色，一邊正常，一邊紅（皮膚超薄）<br />\n<br />\n每次沖完浪都用蛾羅納英<br />\n<br />\n間中一次訓覺會不自覺r損（呢樣最無辜）<br />\n<br />\n有試過帶手套訓但係都係會半夜自己除再r<br />\n<br />\n另外屎忽都有呢個情況，又係夜晚就好痕，起身先知損晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb2880686fb8f01af7567e0b2a9152b47f43a1f","tid":156281,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"我幫你奶袋底 包止痕"},{"pid":"4149328329bc8b2a31aea35a5c5a0f983ef22a08","tid":156281,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保持乾爽 沖完涼徹底用毛巾整乾個度<br />\n唔好著緊身褲/底褲<br />\n搽下醫生開俾你既cream (maybe topical antibiotics)<br />\n唔好用手r 好多細菌係手<br />\n<br />\n利申 小學護</blockquote><br />\n會唔會用紙巾印好過毛巾"},{"pid":"94ab1fd547c36be0a99b36bc9e28283b06d8ac28","tid":156281,"uid":36532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保持乾爽 沖完涼徹底用毛巾整乾個度<br />\n唔好著緊身褲/底褲<br />\n搽下醫生開俾你既cream (maybe topical antibiotics)<br />\n唔好用手r 好多細菌係手<br />\n<br />\n利申 小學護</blockquote><br />\n底褲影響好大!<br />\n我上年都係袋底出濕疹,用好多CREAM都係好完又出過<br />\n之後我立定心腸換晒D棉質底褲做麻質boxer,之後到而家都冇翻發過<br />\n<br />\n我都一度以為自己中左椰菜花,仲去左衛生科睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好在個醫生都話只係濕疹,所以嚴重就真係去睇醫生好"},{"pid":"3b1b748ae3533ab6785086027cf8249ecb2a3343","tid":156281,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"真係可以唔著底褲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b70aaeb0bf7b0e3dc25497fc430ac5df1061857","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友佢生左幾年，當時睇過家庭同專科，都係俾藥膏搽，冇為意係類固醇，依家搽到個春袋左右兩截色，一邊正常，一邊紅（皮膚超薄）<br />\n<br />\n每次沖完浪都用蛾羅納英<br />\n<br />\n間中一次訓覺會不自覺r損（呢樣最無辜）<br />\n<br />\n有試過帶手套訓但係都係會半夜自己除再r<br />\n<br />\n另外屎忽都有呢個情況，又係夜晚就好痕，起身先知損晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你想問既問題係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d460149c340a9312965b060381d4b0f1e54f85","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幫你奶袋底 包止痕</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然好正，但我唔係hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8977eee62482f8cf27bffeb0ed8ec7df56e3acdc","tid":156281,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係可以唔著底褲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你以為我講笑，今日真係無着底褲就出左成日街"},{"pid":"9e3c1e3c5c6b9728aff6669adb5ed952c922873f","tid":156281,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}